</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 $\ltlimit{t}{-1}{\dfdx{y}{x}}$
</p>
</li>
    </ol>

    Is this consistent with the graph and the fact that $t$
    represents the slope from the origin to the point $(x,y)$?
    Explain. 
  </p>
</statement>
</task>
</problem>
